              <b>Hard Mode</b>
              <span>Fewer comforts (reduces streaks + high-end masks)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="switch" id="hardSwitch" data-on="false" role="switch" aria-checked="false"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="tL">
              <b>One-Weapon</b>
              <span>Primary only, secondary becomes ‚Äúnone/knife‚Äù</span>
