          Viewers can use the same hosted link.
          <div style="margin-top:10px; padding:10px; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);">
            <b style="color:rgba(234,241,255,.95)">Pro UX move:</b>
